\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Caption Standard

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "fig:Displacement-of-beetles"

\end_inset

Displacement of beetles from release points within 48 h.
 The points at 500 m indicate beetles that flew beyond the range of the
 radio-tracking recievers.
 Difference between medians for beetles released at the two sites (Asan:
 418 m; Yigo: 275 m) are not significantly different (p = 0.36; bootstrap
 resampling with 10,000 iterations).
 Pooled median displacement was 333 m.
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

