\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Caption Standard

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Males.
 Mean per cent emergent weight for male beetles tracked to ground and tree
 top sites were significantly different (87%, 72% respectively; Welch's
 t = 4.174; p = 0.008).
 
\end_layout

